temporarily

84
00:06:36,000 --> 00:06:39,000
One person does what one person does

85
00:06:39,000 --> 00:06:42,000
Actually the young master took the troubles

86
00:06:42,000 --> 00:06:44,000
I will help him

87
00:06:48,000 --> 00:06:51,000
Do you hear me?

88
00:06:51,000 --> 00:06:53,000
I will do what I said

89
00:06:54,000 --> 00:06:55,240
You want to see me?

90
00:06:56,120 --> 00:06:57,120
This is our master.

91
00:06:57,520 --> 00:06:59,120
If you have any requests, just ask.

92
00:06:59,120 --> 00:07:00,120
Your Highness, leave him alone.

93
00:07:00,520 --> 00:07:01,800
I'll kill him.

94
00:07:01,800 --> 00:07:02,960
I'll send you to your death.

95
00:07:02,960 --> 00:07:03,480
Wait.

96
00:07:04,000 --> 00:07:05,320
If you let Quan Zi go,

97
00:07:05,880 --> 00:07:07,200
I, Your Highness, can guarantee

98
00:07:07,760 --> 00:07:09,360
