101
00:07:11,720 --> 00:07:13,080
A man should be loyal to his country.

102
00:07:13,640 --> 00:07:15,600
He can't be trusted.

103
00:07:18,160 --> 00:07:18,880
You can leave.

104
00:07:19,480 --> 00:07:20,080
Yes.

105
00:07:24,000 --> 00:07:25,400
I hope you can keep your word.

106
00:07:25,640 --> 00:07:26,680
Of course.

107
00:07:34,440 --> 00:07:35,440
It's not a trap.

108
00:07:35,680 --> 00:07:36,680
I'm a man of my word.

109
00:07:36,680 --> 00:07:38,280
I'll send you to your death now.

110
00:07:54,000 --> 00:07:54,880
No.

111
00:07:58,960 --> 00:08:00,160
No.

112
00:08:03,640 --> 00:08:04,880
A man should be honest.

113
00:08:05,720 --> 00:08:07,320
I, Lord Chen, will keep my word.

114
00:08:07,600 --> 00:08:09,000
I won't kill innocent people.

115
00:08:09,320 --> 00:08:10,320
Even if I die,

116
00:08:11,000 --> 00:08:12,720
I'll make you understand.

117
00:08:15,960 --> 00:08:16,560
Kneel.

118
00:08:19,480 --> 00:08:21,240
I think you look

119
00:08:21,720 --> 00:08:22,920
extraordinary.

120
00:08:23,480 --> 00:08:24,960
Since you're trying to enter the Ghost Valley,

121
00:08:25,560 --> 00:08:26,960
you must have a plan.

122
00:08:27,800 --> 00:08:30,720
Luckily, you opened the window and said something.

123
00:08:31,880 --> 00:08:33,760
They have many people and many ways.

124
00:08:34,320 --> 00:08:35,400
They can't be selfish.

125
00:08:36,080 --> 00:08:38,640
Life and death are both good and bad.

126
00:08:39,360 --> 00:08:40,200
I'm Li Jianwei.

127
00:08:40,440 --> 00:08:41,320
I was a dancer when I was young.

128
00:08:41,760 --> 00:08:43,160
I was unfortunate to die with my parents.

129
00:08:43,640 --> 00:08:45,240
I was injured by a man who hung me up to watch the wind and water.

130
00:08:46,800 --> 00:08:48,640
He hung you up to watch the wind and water.

131
00:08:48,840 --> 00:08:50,160
Don't believe him.

132
00:08:51,000 --> 00:08:52,080
I'm a man of my word.

133
00:08:52,320 --> 00:08:53,320
I didn't lie.

134
00:08:53,680 --> 00:08:54,520
So?

135
00:08:54,840 --> 00:08:55,720
I saw the mountain,

136
00:08:55,920 --> 00:08:57,400
the water and the medicine.

137
00:08:57,920 --> 00:08:59,560
It must be a hidden treasure.

138
00:08:59,920 --> 00:09:00,680
So,

139
00:09:01,400 --> 00:09:02,720
I had to go up the mountain and grab the ground.

140
00:09:03,800 --> 00:09:05,000
Grab the ground?

141
00:09:05,600 --> 00:09:07,680
I'm afraid you have a misunderstanding.

142
00:09:08,080 --> 00:09:09,840
We're all wild men.

143
00:09:10,360 --> 00:09:13,800
The mountain is not a treasure.

144
00:09:14,480 --> 00:09:16,240
There must be no place for you.

145
00:09:16,880 --> 00:09:18,120
I respect you as a man.

146
00:09:18,480 --> 00:09:20,960
You can go down the mountain tomorrow morning.

147
00:09:21,120 --> 00:09:22,360
Chen Dawang, you're stupid.

148
00:09:22,560 --> 00:09:23,560
You can't let him go down the mountain.

149
00:09:27,760 --> 00:09:29,320
What if I have to stay?

150
00:09:31,000 --> 00:09:32,000
If so,

151
00:09:32,720 --> 00:09:34,560
you should stay alive.

152
00:09:34,960 --> 00:09:35,880
There must be a place for you

153
00:09:36,280 --> 00:09:38,120
to stay when you see the mountain.

154
00:09:46,960 --> 00:09:47,800
Shuzi.

155
00:09:48,240 --> 00:09:49,520
You don't know how to go down the mountain.

156
00:09:49,520 --> 00:09:50,840
You go down the mountain without telling me.

157
00:09:51,120 --> 00:09:52,920
How dare you tie the saint back?

158
00:09:53,240 --> 00:09:54,280
Have you realized your mistake?

159
00:09:54,600 --> 00:09:55,440
Father.

160
00:09:56,040 --> 00:09:58,280
I know my mistake, but I don't accept it.

161
00:09:59,200 --> 00:10:01,080
I was fooled by him for a moment.

162
00:10:01,320 --> 00:10:02,560
But I didn't make any trouble.

163
00:10:02,920 --> 00:10:04,480
Then you still don't know your mistake.

164
00:10:07,960 --> 00:10:09,360
We were together.

165
00:10:09,800 --> 00:10:11,640
We almost didn't contact the outside world.

166
00:10:11,840 --> 00:10:13,480
But you made such a big noise.

167
00:10:13,800 --> 00:10:15,360
Why didn't you let me kill him?

168
00:10:15,760 --> 00:10:17,120
But you let him go down the mountain?

169
00:10:17,760 --> 00:10:19,240
He has a strange background.

170
00:10:19,440 --> 00:10:20,760
His behavior is abnormal.

171
00:10:21,440 --> 00:10:23,040
If you want to find out the truth,

172
00:10:23,440 --> 00:10:25,800
you have to give up the mountain.

173
00:10:26,520 --> 00:10:28,280
You just want to test

174
00:10:28,640 --> 00:10:30,720
his sincerity and determination.

175
00:10:31,200 --> 00:10:32,640
What if he really goes down the mountain?

176
00:10:33,040 --> 00:10:34,720
I'll make him die faster.

177
00:10:35,360 --> 00:10:36,640
The secrets of the Ghost Valley

178
00:10:37,200 --> 00:10:39,120
can't be leaked out.

179
00:10:40,520 --> 00:10:41,360
Really?

180
00:10:41,680 --> 00:10:43,120
I thought you were old.

181
00:10:46,680 --> 00:10:48,320
I've told you many times.

182
00:10:49,080 --> 00:10:50,960
You need to calm down and think.

183
00:10:52,480 --> 00:10:54,360
You act recklessly every day.

184
00:10:55,120 --> 00:10:57,040
What if you make a mistake?

185
00:10:57,760 --> 00:10:59,040
How can you

186
00:10:59,720 --> 00:11:01,440
make up for the death?

187
00:12:18,320 --> 00:12:21,320
The mountain is praying in the dream.

188
00:12:21,320 --> 00:12:24,800
The wind blows through the ice.

189
00:12:25,040 --> 00:12:29,400
The lonely heaven and earth are all dark.

190
00:12:29,400 --> 00:12:33,920
The mountain doesn't stop the past.